node.text:
Omggg, i can’t believe how easy and fun it was to make these. This is my favorite paleta flavor so now that I’ve mastered it I’m gonna be making them all the time. 

Thank you to @cheilitaschamoy for working with us on this igtv and also hooking you guys up with a discount code so you can save some $$$ on your order of Cheilitas Chamoy or candy! 

use my code ILUVSARAHII to get the Mini Bottle Pack (all 7 flavors) for $25.50!

Ingredients:
Cucumber 
Sugar 
Sea salt 
Tequila (optional) 
Cheilitas Chamoy 
Tajín 
Popsicle Molds

#iluvsarahii #ad

node.text:
For the longest time I didn’t know how to make this but WOW it was so easy and most importantly so tasty. Ps. If you don’t drink, no worries we also made a virgin one on here as well! 

Shout out to @cheilitaschamoy for working with us on this igtv and also hooking you guys up with a discount code so you can save some $$$ on your order. 

use my code ILUVSARAHII on their: 
Mini Pack which consist of all 5oz chamoys for $30. ( free shipping not included) 
Or 
"El Pari Pack", includes all 7 flavors in 5oz and 4 gummies. Regular Price $50.00 with the discount total its $42.50(free shipping) 

Here are the ingredients:
2 cups of Frozen Mango 
1 cup Jumex Mango Nectar 
1 whole lime
Tajin 
Reposado Tequila 
Cheilitas Mango Chamoy

#iluvsarahii #ad

node.text: I have been itching to do a double graphic liner and this is the perfect product to achieve the look. It may look hard but the rich cushiony formula glides right on making it easy to build and blend out. This cream eyeshadow is infused with primer so it lasts for 24hours leaving a matte finish that won’t transfer, fade, smudge or sweat off. It’s also a multi-use product that you can use even on your brows and cheeks! #SmashboxPartner #AlwaysOnSmashbox

node.text:
who else is loving this look?! It’s so easy to recreate and today I want to teach you guys how to achieve it using my Sweet Oasis Palette from @morphebrushes. 
I love how versatile this Palette is, I can create a bold bright eye or a neutral look like this with a pop of blue ! Let me know what you guys think. The Palette goes live on ULTA 2/14 & available on Morphe.com (use code iluvsarahii)

#iluvsarahii #morphepartner #morphesweetoasis

node.title: Neutral eye with a pop of blue🔥

node.text: Hello gorgeous, this is your daily reminder to not forget your SPF🧴When it comes to my skin and body care, SPF is the most important thing I wear. I love lathering my body in @bondisands Fragrance Free SPF 50 Body Sunscreen. This product is packed with so much hydration that lasts for 72hrs and it deeply moisturizes my body while protecting my skin from harmful UVA and UVBS. Now available at @walgreens #bondisands #bondisandssuncare #ad

node.text:
A quick transition from Day to Night using @buxomcosmetics x @ash_kholm palette 🎨 
I love a palette that has it all and Ash really did that 👏🏼 There are 12 neutral and jewel tone colors that are all primer-infused, packed with pigment and a blend of matte, satin, and metallic finishes. 
 
For the neutral look I started with shades UNFILTED, TEDDY and STACKS, then I added RICH RICH and SMOKIN’ for my night look. Which team are you, Day or Night? 
 
@ultabeauty #BUXOMbabe #buxompartner

node.text:
Omggg, i can’t believe how easy and fun it was to make these. This is my favorite paleta flavor so now that I’ve mastered it I’m gonna be making them all the time. 

Thank you to @cheilitaschamoy for working with us on this igtv and also hooking you guys up with a discount code so you can save some $$$ on your order of Cheilitas Chamoy or candy! 

use my code ILUVSARAHII to get the Mini Bottle Pack (all 7 flavors) for $25.50!

Ingredients:
Cucumber 
Sugar 
Sea salt 
Tequila (optional) 
Cheilitas Chamoy 
Tajín 
Popsicle Molds
